**TITLE:** Text goes off screen on Microsoft Edge

**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Go to https://todolistme.net/
2. Input a new task with more than 300 characters
3. Hit Enter

**Expected Result:**
Text goes to a new line when it hits the edge of the to do list area box.

**Actual Result**
Text appears to go off screen and is not visible.

**Environment:**
- Browswer: Microsoft Edge
- OS: Windows 11 Pro
- 
